              <br> With respect, Scratch&Win team</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="footer">
    <div class="stay-in-touch"><p>Stay in touch</p></div>
    <div class="social-container">
      <div class="social-icon">
        <img src="https://s3.eu-central-1.amazonaws.com/www.brosweb.co/facebook.png" alt="" />
      </div>
      <div class="social-icon">
        <img src="https://s3.eu-central-1.amazonaws.com/www.brosweb.co/tweeter.png" alt="" />
      </div>
  
      <div class="social-icon">
        <img src="https://s3.eu-central-1.amazonaws.com/www.brosweb.co/insta.png" alt="" />
